##          one-page markdown report from 16.1B/16.1C outputs.
## Inputs (created earlier under vcell/derived):
##   • sim/*.csv            — timecourses per scenario
##   • sum/all_summaries.tsv, intestinal_deltas.tsv, qa_checks.tsv
